headline: Member Loyalty Group Names Drew Wolff as Treasurer of the Board
summary: VERNON HILLS, Ill., September 29, 2025--Member Loyalty Group, a provider of member experience analytics and strategic support exclusively for credit unions, has announced the appointment of Drew Wolff to its Board of Directors, where he will also serve as Treasurer. Wolff brings more than 25 years of global financial leadership experience across the financial services, consumer and nonprofit sectors.
